If you think your morning oatmeal has to be sweet, think again because @tallulahalexandra delivers on the savory breakfast side with her 2 Minute Savory Oatmeal Bowl, topped with Tillamook Sharp Cheddar Slices and a poached egg. Find the recipe below and pick up Tillamook Cheddar near you at Tillamaps.com. 

-- 

Â½ cup quick cook rolled oats 
Â¾ cup chicken bone broth 
1 @Tillamook Farmstyle Thick Cut Sharp Cheddar Slice 
1 large egg, poached 
Salt and pepper to taste 
Hot sauce + sesame seeds (optional) 

In a microwave safe bowl combine oats and broth then season to taste. Microwave for 60 seconds, then remove bowl from microwave and give oats a gentle stir. Top with @Tillamook Extra Sharp Cheddar Slice then microwave for an additional 30 seconds. 
. 
. 
.
